text: Pauline Lee Hanson (n√©e Seccombe, formerly Zagorski; born 27 May 1954) is an Australian politician. She is the founder and leader of One Nation, a right- wing political party. She has been a Senator for Queensland since 2016, She was re-elected at the 2022 federal election. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Queensland Category:Pauline Hanson's One Nation
